title: GoPro: Fiji Barrels with Bruno Santos - GoPro of the World July Winner
description:
Bruno Santos pulls into a double overhead barrel at Fiji's Cloudbreak and takes home $1,000, a GoPro HERO4, and a year subscription to Surfline.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music
Bacao Rhythm & Steel Band
"Tender Trap"
